# F03: Read Tracking & Compliance

## Summary

This area covers the per-announcement read report (who has viewed and when, Growth+) and Mandatory Confirmation ("Read and Understood", Professional only) that creates a compliance-ready audit trail. Primary actors are Owners and Admins (who read the reports) and Members (who confirm). Read tracking is the core upgrade hook for Growth; Mandatory Confirmation is the Professional compliance differentiator and is P2 — include if time allows, otherwise fast-follow.
